snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - 5 Star Racing [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
Published by Phoenix Games, 5 Star Racing contains five types of racing games, with two tracks each. I think what Phoenix Games meant by "5 Star Racing" is that each of the car types got 1 star reviews, so they thought it was the same thing 'cause the math checks out.

Published by Phoenix Games
Developed by Kung Fu Ltd.
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
